{"tid":2061674,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"求救!鸚鵡魚個頭多左兩個窿!","createTime":"2020-06-12T14:19:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T14:40:35.000Z","uid":34924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"248427a76ebca12fab3a6ed0bf6b79001aaf4474","tid":2061674,"uid":34924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T14:19:07.000Z","msg":"唔好意思第一次開 post 唔知開得啱唔啱<br />\n頭先望望下條魚發現個頭多左兩個窿 <br />\n上網搵過係咪叫頭洞病? 可以點樣處理?<br />\n佢又食得又玩得 都唔為意有啲咩事<br />\n會唔會其實已經好大獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9gibdfa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9gibdfa.jpg&h=75c9564b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9a1fe01db617102d1b2c62df8ee438a2711fcf79","tid":2061674,"uid":40908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T14:21:47.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"2def55ec232e2af42684aff3016d4c70f9049609","tid":2061674,"uid":40272,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T14:22:03.000Z","msg":"傻鳩無鼻點呼吸"},{"pid":"b67bd88ad5326a138455de325321da407ef11fd0","tid":2061674,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T14:23:05.000Z","msg":"可能有武漢肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd44374ca245ff8a36f33ee018e9071c5c178918","tid":2061674,"uid":34924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T14:23:38.000Z","msg":"認真求救 唔想佢死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7368ea252e18304206fa752fd9cb06d88f731a28","tid":2061674,"uid":278168,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"2def55ec232e2af42684aff3016d4c70f9049609","tid":2061674,"uid":40272,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T14:22:03.000Z","msg":"傻鳩無鼻點呼吸"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T14:23:44.000Z","msg":"魚係用鰓呼吸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰個的確係鼻哥窿，但唔係用嚟呼吸，係要嚟聞嘢"},{"pid":"671b3ce0